aweme_info.desc: Did you know you can use AI to help you build iPhone apps similar to how you would web apps? The set up is surprisingly simple — download Xcode, connect it to cursor and start prompting for the Swift code.  While fully bringing a mobile app to life is more extensive, including requiring an Apple Developer account and App Store Approval,  the barrier of entry to get started building has been completely slashed #mobileapps #Cursor #iOs #Xcode
